flowchart LR
    Client[客户端] --> Gateway[API Gateway]

    subgraph API["seckill-api"]
        Handler[HTTP Handler<br/>参数校验/请求超时]
        Admission[Semaphore<br/>本地准入]
        Service[Submit Service]
        RedisRepo[Redis Repository<br/>Lua 封装]
        Publisher[RocketMQ Producer<br/>进程级复用]
    end

    Gateway --> Handler
    Handler --> Admission
    Admission --> Service
    Service --> RedisRepo
    Service --> Publisher

    RedisRepo --> RedisPool[go-redis 连接池]
    RedisPool --> Redis[(Redis Cluster)]
    Publisher --> MQ[(RocketMQ)]

    subgraph Worker["order-worker"]
        Puller[SimpleConsumer Puller]
        Slots[Inflight Semaphore]
        Queue[有界 jobs Channel]
        Workers[固定 Worker Pool]
        Processor[Order Processor]
        PGRepo[pgx Repository]
    end

    MQ --> Puller
    Puller --> Slots
    Slots --> Queue
    Queue --> Workers
    Workers --> Processor
    Processor --> PGRepo
    PGRepo --> PGPool[pgxpool]
    PGPool --> PG[(PostgreSQL Primary)]
    Workers -->|提交成功后 ACK| MQ

    subgraph Query["query-api"]
        QueryHandler[Query Handler]
        QueryLimiter[独立 Semaphore]
        ResultRepo[Result Repository]
    end

    Client --> QueryHandler
    QueryHandler --> QueryLimiter
    QueryLimiter --> ResultRepo
    ResultRepo --> Redis
    ResultRepo -.最终状态回源.-> PG

    Metrics[Metrics / Logs / Trace] --- API
    Metrics --- Worker
    Admin[独立管理端口<br/>pprof/health/readiness] --- API
    Admin --- Worker
